#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/downloads.adoc:4
msgid "Videos and practice files for the course may be downloaded from this page. Or if you prefer, the videos and files are linked individually throughout the course as they occur in the curriculum."
